---
title: Sirloin Steak & Miso Butter with Sesame Veggies & Crispy Onion Mash
description: Serve an elegant meal with a dash of Japanese flair. Umami- rich miso paste adds an unmistakable depth of flavour to a perfectly cooked steak while a toasted sesame dressing lifts quickly sautéed vegetables to brand new heights. Every bite of this easy steak dinner is simply sensational!

*Keep an eye out...Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
